      <td class="govuk-table__cell">Assign Enterprise Architect</td>
      <td class="govuk-table__cell">Assign Enterprise Architect and identify other architects (e.g. security, solution or technical architects) to collaborate with</td>
      <td class="govuk-table__cell">Lead Enterprise Architect, Architecture Review Co-ordinator</td>
