      </td>
      <td class="govuk-table__cell">Delivery Manager, Architecture Review Co-ordinator</td>
    </tr>
    <tr class="govuk-table__row">
      <td class="govuk-table__cell">6</td>
      <td class="govuk-table__cell">Seek support as needed</td>
      <td class="govuk-table__cell">
        Ongoing collaboration between Enterprise Architecture and delivery team
      </td>
      <td class="govuk-table__cell">Enterprise Architect, Lead Developer, Delivery Manager</td>
    </tr>
    <tr class="govuk-table__row">
      <td class="govuk-table__cell">7</td>
      <td class="govuk-table__cell">Prepare Architecture Report</td>
      <td class="govuk-table__cell">
